      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein dampers and refreshed polyurethane bushings, maintaining sharp turn-in and composure. While showing minor cosmetic patina typical of its age, the mechanical vitals\u2014including recent valve clearances and rod bearing inspection\u2014are well within enthusiast standards. A mechanically sound platform ready for the canyon or the track.",
